			<div class="post-7759 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-bitcoin-2 tag-200-day-moving-average tag-200dma tag-bitcoin tag-cryptographic-hash tag-laws-of-mathematics tag-total-finder post_box top" id="post-7759">
